data.description: Exquisite 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath 2-Story Home in Charming Rosharon, TX this residence offers an impressive blend of spaciousness, style, and comfort. The primary bedroom suite, located on the first floor, offers a private retreat. With an en-suite bathroom boasting a spa-like soaking tub, a separate shower, dual sinks, and a spacious walk-in closet, this suite provides a harmonious blend of luxury and comfort. Upstairs you'll find three additional generously sized bedrooms, each offering its own unique charm and versatility. A second full bathroom accommodates the needs of the upper level. Outdoor living takes center stage in the expansive backyard, where endless possibilities await. Create a serene oasis for relaxation, set up a play area for the kids, or design your ideal outdoor entertainment space – the choice is yours. Schedule your showing today and seize the chance to make this remarkable 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath residence your own. The life you've been dreaming of awaits!
